comment._content: Biography of missionary Benjamin Yates Ashwell from the 1966 Encyclopaedia of NZ: www.teara.govt.nz/en/1966/ashwell-benjamin-yates The Kaitotehe pā was was once home of the Māori King Potatau Te Wherowhero.
